data.description: Check out this charming 3 bedroom, 2 bath cottage near downtown Brownsville! This cozy home boasts a recently remodeled kitchen with brand-new cabinets and granite countertops, new water heater, updated plumbing, and original hardwood floors. New roof was installed in 2018. Enjoy the convenience of a detached carport and the security of a fenced yard. Don't miss this gem in a prime location!
